@startuml UC1: Place Order - Low Stock Error

!theme plain

autonumber

actor User
participant "System" as System
participant "Server" as Server

== Menu Selection ==

User -> System: Press "Select Menu"
System -> User: Display OrderUI

== Order Process ==

User -> System: Press "Select Dinner"
System -> System: Save Dinner
System -> User: Display ServeStyle

User -> System: Press "Select ServeStyle"
System -> User: Display Additional Options

User -> System: Adjust Quantity
User -> System: Press "Select"
System -> Server: Request Order Creation

Server -> Server: Check Inventory
Server -> Server: Validate Inventory Capacity\n(Check maximum capacity per window)

Server -> Server: Reserved Quantity + Requested Quantity > Capacity

Server -> System: Low Stock Error\n("Insufficient stock" or\n"Exceeds maximum capacity per window")

System -> User: Display Error Message\n("Insufficient stock")

@enduml
